highlights.text: “Babblarnas vaggvisa” by Babblarna has been on Top Songs Sweden the longest, at 353 weeks straight.
“TIT FOR TAT” by Tate McRae is the highest new entry on Top Songs Sweden at #11.
Josefine Götestam has the most spots on Top Songs Sweden. “Djurens vaggvisa” is the highest at #2.
“Pink Skies” by Zach Bryan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Sweden, up 68 spots at #104.
